com.fluidops.ajax.components

Class FPageComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fluidops.ajax.components.FComponent
      • com.fluidops.ajax.components.FContainer
        • com.fluidops.ajax.components.FPageComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEventListener

    public class FPageComponent
extends FContainer
    Wraps FPage into an FContainer. many UI components are directly linked to FPages such as IpPoolCreationWizard for example. FPage extends FContainer, but methods around computing its depth and the populateView / render behaviour require an FPage to be the root node in the page, container, component tree. As a consequence, things that extend from FPage are not really reusable in other contexts (e.g. as an INT widget) This class takes an FPage, runs its initialization and then "steals" its children, making them its own, thereby allowing FPage implementations to be reused as containers
    Author:
    aeb
